              </h2>
              <p class="pera-subtitle mb-15">
                The act of giving is deeply rooted in the essence of Ramadan in the form of Zakat, Fidya Kaffarah, Fitrana and etc. It is a month that teaches compassion, patience, and the importance of sharing with others in Islam. However, for many families, observing Ramadan can be challenging due to financial problems and more. That's where your Ramadan donation plays a crucial role.

              </p>
              <p class="pera-subtitle"></p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-10 mt-10">
              <a
                href="https://crf-donate.tscube.co.in/"
                class="btn btn-primary-fill">Donate Now</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Second Div: Heading and Paragraph -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container mt-5">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-between align-items-center">
          <div class="col-md-7 mb-4 align-self-center" style="padding-left: 20px;">
            <div class="section-tittle mb-35">
              
              <h2 class="title font-700 pb-15">CRF's Ramadan Appeal: <br> How We Make a Difference


              </h2>
              <p class="pera-subtitle mb-15">
                CRF has been at the forefront of Ramadan charity for years, working tirelessly to support communities in need. Our Ramadan Appeal 2025 is here to maximize the impact of your generosity, ensuring that every donation of yours reaches those who need it the most.



              </p>
              
              <p class="pera-subtitle"></p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-10 mt-10">
              <a
                href="https://crf-donate.tscube.co.in/"
                class="btn btn-primary-fill">Donate Now</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-md-5 mb-4 mb-md-0" style="padding-left: 20px;">
            <img
              src="/assets/images/appeals/sadaqah-4.jpg"
              alt="Rounded Image"
              class="img-fluid rounded"
            />
          </div>
          <section class="helpful-area-three section-padding">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="row g-24">
                <div class="col-xl-3 col-md-6 col-lg-6">
