                    <div class="helpful-card-caption">
                      <h4 class="caption-title" style="background-color: white !important; color:black">Ramadan Food Packs</h4>
                      <p class="caption-para px-4">
                        Each Food Pack is thoughtfully prepared with essential items to meet diverse dietary needs, supporting underprivileged families in preparing nutritious meals throughout Ramadan.
                      </p>
                 
                    </div>
                    <div class="number-watermark" style="color: rgba(221, 221, 221, 0.1) !important;">
                      <h4 class="number" style="color: rgba(221, 221, 221, 0.1) !important;">01</h4>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-xl-3 col-md-6 col-lg-6">
                  <div class="helpful-card wow fadeInUp custom-shadow "  data-wow-delay="0.0s">
                    
