                    <div class="helpful-card-caption">
                      <h4 class="caption-title" style="background-color: white !important; color:black">Community-Centered Approach</h4>
                      <p class="caption-para px-4">  
                        <span class="font-weight-bold">We collaborate with local partners in the and have volunteers to identify and reach the most vulnerable families. This ensures that your donation has a direct and meaningful impact.
      
       
      
                      </p>
                 
                    </div>
                    <div class="number-watermark" style="color: rgba(221, 221, 221, 0.1) !important;">
                      <h4 class="number" style="color: rgba(221, 221, 221, 0.1) !important;">03</h4>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xl-3 col-md-6 col-lg-6">
                  <div class="helpful-card wow fadeInUp custom-shadow "  data-wow-delay="0.0s">
                  
                    <div class="helpful-card-caption">
                      <h4 class="caption-title" style="background-color: white !important; color:black">Transparency and Accountability</h4>
                      <p class="caption-para px-4">  
                        <span class="font-weight-bold">At CRF, we value your trust. We provide detailed reports and updates so you can see how and where your Ramadan donation is making a difference.
      
            
      
                      </p>
                   
                    </div>
                    <div class="number-watermark" style="color: rgba(221, 221, 221, 0.1) !important;">
                      <h4 class="number" style="color: rgba(221, 221, 221, 0.1) !important;">04</h4>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
               
              </div>
            </div>
