          Ramadan Timetable 2025
        </h2>
        <p class="pb-2">
          Stay organized and plan your prayers, Suhoor, and Iftar with our
          detailed Ramadan timetable to make the most of this holy month.
        </p>
        <div class="text-center pt-4">
          <a href="/assets/crf-ramadan-calendar.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn-primary-fill pill-btn">
            <span
              ><svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="16"
                height="16"
                fill="currentColor"
                class="bi bi-download"
                viewBox="0 0 16 16"
              >
                <path
                  d="M.5 9.9a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v2.5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h12a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-2.5a.5.5 0 0 1 1 0v2.5a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H2a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-2.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5"
                ></path>
                <path
                  d="M7.646 11.854a.5.5 0 0 0 .708 0l3-3a.5.5 0 0 0-.708-.708L8.5 10.293V1.5a.5.5 0 0 0-1 0v8.793L5.354 8.146a.5.5 0 1 0-.708.708z"
