          <div class="section-tittle mb-35">
            
            <h2 class="title font-700 pb-15">Ways to Donate in Ramadan 2025

            </h2>
            <p class="pera-subtitle mb-15">
              Making a Ramadan donation through CRF is simple and flexible. We’ve made the process easy so that you can focus on the joy of giving. Here are the ways you can contribute to our Ramadan Appeal 2025


            </p>
            <ol class=" list-group-numbered " style="padding-left: 0px !important;">
              <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Online Donations:</strong> Visit our <a href="/" class="text-primary text-decoration-underline">secure website</a> to make your contribution. Choose from a range of donation options, including Food Packs, Iftar Boxes, or general support for Ramadan 2025.
              </li>
              <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Monthly Contributions:</strong> Set up a recurring donation to extend your impact beyond Ramadan. This ensures continuous support for families in need throughout the year.
              </li>
              <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Corporate Sponsorships:</strong> Businesses can partner with CRF to sponsor large-scale distributions. This is a great way to fulfill corporate social responsibility while making a significant impact.
              </li>
              <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Zakat Donations:</strong> Fulfill your Zakat obligation by contributing to our Ramadan Appeal. Our zakat appeal aligns with the principles of Zakat, ensuring your donation is used in the most effective way. You can <a href="/appeals/zakat-calculator" class="text-primary text-decoration-underline">calculate your zakat</a> as well to understand the exact amount to pay.
              </li>
              <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Spread the Word:</strong> Even if you're unable to donate, you can support our cause by sharing our Ramadan Appeal with your friends and family. Together, we can create an impactful effect of kindness.
              </li>
            </ol>
            <p class="pera-subtitle"></p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-10 mt-10">
            <a
              href="https://crf-donate.tscube.co.in/"
              class="btn btn-primary-fill">Donate Now</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 mb-4 mb-md-0" style="padding-left: 20px;">
          <img
            src="/assets/images/appeals/sadaqah-4.jpg"
            alt="Rounded Image"
            class="img-2 rounded"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
  <div
    class="section-tittle mb-50 container p-2 mt-4"
    style="text-align: center;"
  >
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <h2 class="title font-700" style="color: #156E9D;">
          Make a Positive Impact with Your Ramadan Charity  
        </h2>

