          class="col-md-6 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-center"
        >
          <p class="lead">
             <span style="font-weight: 700; color:black;">A Mother's Gratitude:</span> Last Ramadan, your donations helped Tasleem, a widowed mother of three, who had no means to provide Iftar for her children. With the support of CRF's Food Pack program, Tasleem's family was able to observe Ramadan with dignity and peace of mind.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Right column -->
        <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
          <p class="lead">
           <span style="font-weight: 700; color:black;">Empowering Communities:</span>In rural areas where food insecurity is rampant, our Iftar Boxes have brought communities together. The meals not only nourish but also create a sense of belonging and togetherness during this sacred month.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
